This issue is related to the [other bug](https://github.com/FasterXML/jackson-dataformat-xml/issues/86) but the reporter closed the issue after he found a workaround. I'll probably end up doing the same to resolve our issue but it would be ideal if we could get this fix ported into 2.11 if possible. Thanks!
